@luke_hacks_HostAddress = http://localhost:5149

### Register
POST {{luke_hacks_HostAddress}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST {{luke_hacks_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Current user
GET {{luke_hacks_HostAddress}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###
